    "description": "This game is a simple and highly challenging 2D puzzle game with a system similar to &quot;Sokoban,&quot; in which the player moves boxes to secure a path to the goal.<br><br>As you progress, gimmicks are added, such as &quot;unlocking a passageway with a key,&quot; &quot;shooting arrows to destroy balloon objects,&quot; &quot;disappearing blocks that disappear once you get on them,&quot; &quot;transfer gates connecting two points,&quot; &quot;elevating blocks that switch with arrows,&quot; and &quot;interlocking tags that move another box together when you move a box. Gimmicks are added to the game.<br><br>If you get stuck, you can share the stage codes set for each stage with your friends, allowing each of you to play the same stage regardless of your progress.<br><br>This game is a fan game for the archer 🏹 Ieiri Popo of the Vtuber unit &quot;HIYOCRO&quot;.<br><br>BGM is provided by &quot;DOVA-SYNDROME&quot;, a music material site.<br>Sound effect creation software &quot;sfxr&quot; is used.<br><br>[About the distribution of gameplay videos]<br>No report is required when distributing gameplay videos.<br>Please note that we are not responsible for any damage caused by the actual game play and distribution.",
